{"tid":1595542,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"78歲嬤寺廟「採果實」慘遭硬上　和尚持刀性侵完竟道謝","createTime":"2019-09-26T06:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T08:32:52.000Z","uid":225846,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b7ac2ec43c6eed36c37abf6b01375ab025a9321c","tid":1595542,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3956/3956737.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3956%2F3956737.jpg&h=c8371f6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲警方到場後，禪房內早已空無一人，只剩一個枕頭掉落在地上。（圖／翻攝自thethaiger）<br />\n<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n泰國驚傳有出家僧侶竟性侵上廟裡採果實的78歲老婦人，大犯淫戒。被害阿嬤表示，這名40多歲的和尚看到她後，突然拿刀挾持，逼她就範，甚至在性侵得逞後，轉頭跟她說「謝謝」，才逃離現場。據了解，該名婦人與丈夫一同住在該間寺廟附近，當天只是想要採摘果實，怎知竟會發生憾事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3956/3956738.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3956%2F3956738.jpg&h=11170dc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據泰媒報導，這名78歲的阿嬤日前到離家400公尺遠的一間寺廟撿拾果實，沒想到才剛走進寺廟，馬上被一名目測為40多歲的中年和尚持刀威脅，並將她逼近寺廟內的一間禪房內，隨後性侵阿嬤。沒想到和尚性侵得逞後，竟還轉頭向老阿嬤說謝謝，行為十分囂張。<br />\n<br />\n阿嬤雖然感到十分驚恐，但事發後仍然勇敢地馬上到醫院進行體檢，並向警方報案。警方調查後發現，該名嫌犯約在10天前搬到寺廟居住，沒有人知道他的姓名與確切身分。警方趕往老婦人所說的寺廟後，寺廟早已人去樓空，禪房內甚至只剩一個枕頭掉在地上。警方有意傳其他證人到案，以追蹤該名和尚的確切行蹤與背景。"},{"pid":"2239b23db7e70cf1a6abc2896cdb917523984874","tid":1595542,"uid":15605,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:09:34.000Z","msg":"衲dee幾時去咗泰國"},{"pid":"52ff3e1de3570f1bed48f1eebde0cc4aabe4839a","tid":1595542,"uid":50161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:09:38.000Z","msg":"少女唔愛鋤阿婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a19f005e8432f817e1472940934a48cd5a5b16","tid":1595542,"uid":69741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:12:48.000Z","msg":"禁慾禁得耐咪搞成咁囉，正常人點會緊火緊到阿婆都插，仲要插個就嚟八十路既"},{"pid":"7866a44fd28d1a4e36cee5a492659e8ed261400b","tid":1595542,"uid":119456,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:15:56.000Z","msg":"耆齡王"},{"pid":"258d4990c4f51d15079a0335041112dfa078f742","tid":1595542,"uid":100150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2239b23db7e70cf1a6abc2896cdb917523984874","tid":1595542,"uid":15605,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:09:34.000Z","msg":"衲dee幾時去咗泰國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:29:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec6280ed2dca8767a305b747cc6f91114a6393c","tid":1595542,"uid":21394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:30:59.000Z","msg":"係咪d降頭野，採集材料開壇"},{"pid":"075afef257c44da5ec52a1a3e2e59f3c2f476941","tid":1595542,"uid":225846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fec6280ed2dca8767a305b747cc6f91114a6393c","tid":1595542,"uid":21394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:30:59.000Z","msg":"係咪d降頭野，採集材料開壇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:31:50.000Z","msg":"落降頭需要嘔吐物？"},{"pid":"7929b73e8d5e7c2dec250f24518170e52ca58a57","tid":1595542,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52ff3e1de3570f1bed48f1eebde0cc4aabe4839a","tid":1595542,"uid":50161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:09:38.000Z","msg":"少女唔愛鋤阿婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:32:52.000Z","msg":"？？？"}]}